name: Bustier, g-string and stockings with skull print.
description:
Bustier, g-string and stockings with skull print.
Just let me know what size you need.

Standard Estimated Shipping Rates & Fees 
Please keep in mind these rates are estimated and will cover majority of our items. Large orders, Irregular shape order or purchases that include shoes may incur a slightly higher shipping charge.  All shipping charges will be displayed at our checkout screen for your viewing 
Shipping & Handling to the U.S. via U.S.P.S. Priority Mail  
The first item is $6.00 
Each additional item to the same address is $1.50 
Shipping & Handling to the U.S. via First Class Mail 
The first item is $2.50* (Not available on all items, see available shipping charges at the checkout screen.  Multiple orders being shipped to same address with shipping charges of $6.00 and $2.50.  The highest shipping cost will be charge on the first item and second item will be charge $1.50.) 
Each additional item to the same address is $1.50 
Shipping & Handling to Canada via U.S.P.S. Air Mail* 
The first item is $7.00 
Each additional item to the same address is $2.50 
Shipping & Handling International via U.S.P.S. Air Mail* 
The first item is $12.00 
Each additional item to the same address is $2.50 
 
 
Our preferred shipping carrier is the United States Postal Service,  For U.S. orders, majority of our items are shipped Priority Mail and a select few of our items (such as pantyhose, thongs, bra's)  are shipped First Class Mail.  They can be easily detected by the shipping charge of $2.50 for the first item and 1.50 for each additional item.   

* International Shipping rates can vary by country as well as the final weight and dimensions of the package. Therefore, International shipping rates are subject to increase based on the current rates for the destination country.
